    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/23656887ed5842fed60509da9477df78.poster.avif?t=1686553863\" width=290 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/23656887ed5842fed60509da9477df78.webm?t=1686553863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/23656887ed5842fed60509da9477df78.mp4?t=1686553863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>青鸟乐园是一款AVG+互动解谜的恐怖游戏。<br>上篇包含两个章节，包含剧院与鬼屋。<br>章节里每小关都有不同种的游戏方式。<br><br>游戏中，有精彩刺激的互动解谜、引人入胜的剧情，<br>也有诡异惊悚的画面表现，让我们与一个个迷人的角色，<br>一同沉浸在危险的乐园中!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/7869f09d51c652a36a559be1b63eb271.poster.avif?t=1686553863\" width=290 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/7869f09d51c652a36a559be1b63eb271.webm?t=1686553863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/7869f09d51c652a36a559be1b63eb271.mp4?t=1686553863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>★互动解谜关卡设计不重复，每关都是新的惊奇。<br>★一万字以上的丰富剧情。<br>★美术风格化，使用乐园、马戏团、朴克牌等西方奇幻元素。<br>★画面与音乐结合带来沉浸式的享受。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/d57b58714fb1803b419a02c39dc4c189.avif?t=1686553863\" width=200 height=66 /></span><br><br>有缘的人能随着青鸟使者来到青鸟乐园。只要你抵押灵魂作为赌注，<br>青鸟乐园能帮你杀死一个人。女孩薇薇娜，带着坚定的意志踏进了乐园<br>，挑战各种恶魔设下的奇异关卡。<br><br>她能不能实现愿望并赢回灵魂，离开乐园迎接黎明呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/a16eb7891eeff57a30428491fb359694.avif?t=1686553863\" width=200 height=66 /></span><br><br>  您好，我是残月C.moon，台湾人。<br>  成立一人工作室:黑光游戏工作室，进行独立游戏的开发。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/1f7f9c0da1e5ab143093c6fd8eb52ef2.poster.avif?t=1686553863\" width=222 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/1f7f9c0da1e5ab143093c6fd8eb52ef2.webm?t=1686553863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/1f7f9c0da1e5ab143093c6fd8eb52ef2.mp4?t=1686553863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>【上篇】<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/0a8949c6f4a246c9efcecc758c7d6c36.avif?t=1686553863\" width=300 height=100 /></span><br><br>乐园里十分热闹，薇薇娜却被一处安静的角落吸引。<br>那是一座剧院，颜色有些黯淡古典，十分的安静。<br><br>魔术师在里面，等着他的猎物。<br><br>小丑与魁儡戏谑的笑着，设下邪恶的诡计与困难的谜题。<br>女孩会在此失败吗?她究竟能不能躲过被暗影吞噬的命运呢?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/a9c180dfd148cf2f665ce4e6ee566122.avif?t=1686553863\" width=300 height=100 /></span><br><br>通关了剧院后，薇薇娜站在诡异洋宅的大门前。<br>那是一间有点破旧的阴森洋宅。<br><br>她看见许多昆虫的影子，听见节肢伸展的声音。<br>鬼魂们一闪而逝，低声呢喃着悼词。<br><br>男孩打开鬼屋的门，邀请来客进入。<br><br>【下篇】<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/50fcdc01f5cc6372c6d5bf7c02e9a92d.avif?t=1686553863\" width=300 height=100 /></span><br><br>少女哼着歌。<br>少女缝着娃娃。<br>少女朝着薇薇娜笑了。<br>「成为我的娃娃吧。」<br>「我会好好疼爱妳的。」<br>娃娃屋的娃娃们，将薇薇娜团团围住。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/15b036ee28c430f478c3bc8988d4e21b.avif?t=1686553863\" width=300 height=100 /></span><br><br>薇薇娜相信他对她许下的&quot;承诺&quot;。<br>通过了赌场关卡后，她就能夺回自己的灵魂了。<br><br>但事情真的会如此顺利吗?<br>赌场中的恶魔们狂欢着。<br>其中一个恶魔，带着不怀好意的笑容朝她走来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/254f3ef110c9b38a59296c7ffb402a6a.avif?t=1686553863\" width=300 height=100 /></span><br>★Discord社群(｢･ω･)｢欢迎来聊天<br><br>★Patreon(｡•ㅅ•｡)♡支持我走这里<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1498290/extras/9198e80b478d8827b4c4d6cf57464061.avif?t=1686553863\" width=537 height=302 /></span>",
